article.description: — Eli Lawrence posted 19 points as Middle Tennessee got past UT Martin 73-61 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Lawrence carries Middle Tennessee past UT Martin 73-61
article.linkText: Lawrence carries Middle Tennessee past UT Martin 73-61
article.story: MURFREESBORO, Tenn. -- — Eli Lawrence posted 19 points as Middle Tennessee got past UT Martin 73-61 on Wednesday night. Donovan Sims had 15 points for Middle Tennessee (7-1), which won its fourth consecutive game. Tyler Millin added 11 points. Darius Simmons had 17 points for the Skyhawks (3-5). Koby Jeffries added 11 points. KJ Simon had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
